title: The windows were open
description:
Our story tonight is called “The windows were open” and it’s a story about a sunny summer day by the lake, solitude, and strawberries. It’s also about the feeling of being free from a schedule and deadlines, and about doing some favorite things.

So get cozy and ready to sleep.

Order the book now! hyperurl.co/NothingMuchHappens
